  "body": "# submission name:\r\nadaptive_masking_joint_frame_model\r\n\r\n# upload zipped `archive.zip`\r\n[archive.zip](https://github.com/user-attachments/files/27326003/archive.zip)\r\n\r\n# report.txt\r\n```\r\n=== Evaluation config ===\r\n  batch_size: 16\r\n  device: cuda\r\n  num_threads: 2\r\n  prefetch_queue_depth: 4\r\n  report: /root/comma_video_compression_challenge/submissions/adaptive_masking_joint_frame_model/report.txt\r\n  seed: 1234\r\n  submission_dir: /root/comma_video_compression_challenge/submissions/adaptive_masking_joint_frame_model\r\n  uncompressed_dir: /root/comma_video_compression_challenge/videos\r\n  video_names_file: /root/comma_video_compression_challenge/public_test_video_names.txt\r\n=== Evaluation results over 600 samples ===\r\n  Average PoseNet Distortion: 0.00018940\r\n  Average SegNet Distortion: 0.00057185\r\n  Submission file size: 236,328 bytes\r\n  Original uncompressed size: 37,545,489 bytes\r\n  Compression Rate: 0.00629444\r\n  Final score: 100*segnet_dist + √(10*posenet_dist) + 25*rate = 0.26\r\n```\r\n\r\n# does your submission require gpu for evaluation (inflation)?\r\nyes\r\n\r\n# did you include the compression script? and want it to be merged?\r\nno\r\n\r\n# additional comments\r\nexact score `0.25806622496743437`\r\n",
